    2. validation/veloc/scripts/run_parallel_queue.py:1389-1397 — widen silent-no-op guard predicate from `rc == 0` to `rc in (0, 124, 137)` so any future iter producing 0 tokens in <10s wall is caught regardless of how opencode exited (defense-in-depth)
